OL,3,CTourette Scotland demand apology for
OL,4,C'abhorrent' Saturday Night Live sketch
OL,6,FA charity supporting people with
OL,7,FTourette Syndrome has slammed an
OL,8,F"abhorrent and pathetic" sketch that
OL,9,Fwas featured on Saturday Night Live.
OL,11,FTourette Scotland has accused
OL,12,Fexecutives at NBC of reinforcing the
OL,13,F'highly dangerous myth' that Tourette
OL,14,Fsufferers fake their symptoms.
OL,16,FIt has also asked that a full public
OL,17,Fapology is made to John Davidson, and
OL,18,Fthe wider Tourette community.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
