OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1772885577
OL,3,CTourette Scotland demand apology for
OL,4,C'abhorrent' Saturday Night Live sketch
OL,6,FAnd that those working for the network
OL,7,Fare placed on a Tourette Syndrome
OL,8,Fawareness programme.
OL,10,FIt comes in the wake of the backlash
OL,11,Freceived by Tourette campaigner John
OL,12,FDavidson, from Galashiels, who
OL,13,Fexperienced an involuntary verbal tic
OL,14,Fat the BAFTAs last month.
OL,16,FThe 54 year old was attending the
OL,17,Fawards ceremony as the film 'I Swear,'
OL,18,Fwhich tells the story of his life and
OL,19,Fyears of campaigning to raise
OL,20,Fawareness of the condition, was up for
OL,21,Fseveral awards.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
