FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1772885577
OL,3,CTourette Scotland demand apology for
OL,4,C'abhorrent' Saturday Night Live sketch
OL,6,FHe was heard shouting a racial slur
OL,7,Fwhilst Sinners actors Michael B Jordan
OL,8,Fand Delroy Lindo were on stage,
OL,9,Fsomething which Davidson says he was
OL,10,F"deeply mortified" by.
OL,12,FOn February 28th, Saturday Night Live
OL,13,Fran a skit which depicted a series of
OL,14,Fcelebrities, such as Kanye West, JK
OL,15,FRowling, and Mel Gibson, blaming their
OL,16,F'controversial' behaviour on
OL,17,FTourette's.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
