PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1772885577
OL,3,CTourette Scotland demand apology for
OL,4,C'abhorrent' Saturday Night Live sketch
OL,6,FTourette Scotland called the sketch
OL,7,F"one of the most abhorrent and
OL,8,Fpathetic attempts at satire" they have
OL,9,Fever witnessed, and said it "did
OL,10,Fnothing but attempt to belittle the
OL,11,Fchallenges faced by TS sufferers on a
OL,12,Fdaily basis."
OL,14,FThe organisation has requested that
OL,15,Fthe footage is removed from all media
OL,16,Fsources, and "is purged from the
OL,17,FSaturday Night Live archives" and that
OL,18,F"all members of the SNL executive team
OL,19,Fand writing staff are immediately
OL,20,Fplaced on a suitable Tourette's
OL,21,FSyndrome awareness program."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
